1f5191dd-116a-4524-8726-26cf4d27499e.title: <player>
1f5191dd-116a-4524-8726-26cf4d27499e.text: Well if you're not going to answer, I'll go.

62fb80fc-4e6a-4696-b47e-9a555efae8e0.title: Boy
62fb80fc-4e6a-4696-b47e-9a555efae8e0.text:
I've kicked my ball over that hedge, into that garden!
The old lady who lives there is scary... She's locked the
ball in her wooden shed! Can you get my ball back for
me please?

options.text: Ok, I'll see what I can do.

f2aa5939-39ad-43dc-890b-f1516e475c9c.title: <player>
f2aa5939-39ad-43dc-890b-f1516e475c9c.text: Ok, I'll see what I can do.

4bc5eaf5-bc5b-46a8-8986-71ebd7eb162a.title: Boy
4bc5eaf5-bc5b-46a8-8986-71ebd7eb162a.text: Have you got my ball back yet?

cd0e0982-7939-45d6-bd79-dd9e15fe5a15.title: Boy
cd0e0982-7939-45d6-bd79-dd9e15fe5a15.text: Well, it's in the shed in that garden.

04141aee-873d-43a5-ac35-2d767bba22eb.title: <player>
04141aee-873d-43a5-ac35-2d767bba22eb.text:
Hi, I have got your ball back. It was MUCH harder
than I thought it would be.

13bda729-03f8-4160-b4a6-a1100e0caade.title: Boy
13bda729-03f8-4160-b4a6-a1100e0caade.text: Thank you for getting my ball back!
